  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Humanity's destiny failed. The bacteria PBB-1 discovered on Proxima B shows humans they are not in control of the universe like they once believed. </p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ></h2><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Fight the infected to survive</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >PBB-1 binds to organic material, spreading and devouring all it can. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3197230/extras/51795c5ccad7c9b4675a7fc3c5ee6867.poster.avif?t=1773182694\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3197230/extras/51795c5ccad7c9b4675a7fc3c5ee6867.webm?t=1773182694\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3197230/extras/51795c5ccad7c9b4675a7fc3c5ee6867.mp4?t=1773182694\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >There are a limited number of supplies available when floating through space</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Gather resources, but use them wisely. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3197230/extras/6eccbc3b6252e831d34004d57817902a.poster.avif?t=1773182694\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3197230/extras/6eccbc3b6252e831d34004d57817902a.webm?t=1773182694\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3197230/extras/6eccbc3b6252e831d34004d57817902a.mp4?t=1773182694\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Sneak around infected to avoid using precious ammo</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Choosing not to fight is always an option.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3197230/extras/2c74cc297e3e01625c5a0328e0b99b1f.poster.avif?t=1773182694\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3197230/extras/2c74cc297e3e01625c5a0328e0b99b1f.webm?t=1773182694\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3197230/extras/2c74cc297e3e01625c5a0328e0b99b1f.mp4?t=1773182694\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Explore the 3 stories of The SS Destiny</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >3 floors offering different environments, visuals, supplies, and combat.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3197230/extras/5c945733f1da09311905c502d95c8498.poster.avif?t=1773182694\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3197230/extras/5c945733f1da09311905c502d95c8498.webm?t=1773182694\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3197230/extras/5c945733f1da09311905c502d95c8498.mp4?t=1773182694\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p>",
